Tusk Says Poland to Meet Euro Criteria in 2015, Gazeta Says

-- B y   M a r t a   W a l d o c h
-- 
2011-04-09T10:44:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-09/tusk-says-poland-to-meet-euro-criteria-in-2015-gazeta-says.html
Poland will meet all the criteria
for adopting the euro in 2015 unless “anything exceptional
happens,” though it won’t join the single currency at that
time, Prime Minister  Donald Tusk  said in an interview with
Gazeta Wyborcza.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Marta Waldoch in Warsaw on 
 mwaldoch@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net  